he Sling Orange service offers 30 channels for just $25/mo \u2013 including ESPN, Disney Channel, AMC, TNT, TBS, CNN, A&E, History, and many more.", "short_description": "Sling TV is Live TV, Only Better. The #1 Live TV Streaming Service that lets you personalize your channel lineup and save.\nStart with the service best for you, then pick Extras in your favorite genres: Sports, Comedy, Kids, News, Movies, Lifestyle, Spanish, & more. Change your service online anytime."}]}, "developer_name": "Sling TV, LLC", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.sling.com/offer-details/disclaimers/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.sling.com/offer-details/disclaimers/terms-of-use", "publisher_name": "Sling TV, LLC", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.sling.com/", "category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED", "genres": ["MOVIE", "NEWS_AND_INFORMATION", "SPORTS"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "en_US"], "supported_input_devices": ["GEAR_VR_CONTROLLER"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "CO_EX"], "id": "5196024393755085"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974609_695765217470338_3934964825171427328_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=0KwPg4wjG0oQ7kNvgHcJuED&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AZ2ARI_y_CBhaRGGSz9nBK1&oh=00_AYC1g9qyn7xaxL8zIINJyZ7rD6BUiHUfkfX1dQe0kU4wTw&oe=66D83D62"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Sling TV", "platform": "ANDROID", "context_category": null, "context_topics": [