r just $5\n\nThis is TV on your terms. No paying for useless channels, no long-term contracts, no hidden fees, easy online cancellation.\n\nThe Sling Orange service offers 30 channels for just $25/mo \u2013 including ESPN, Disney Channel, AMC, TNT, TBS, CNN, A&E, History, and many more.", "short_description": "Sling TV is Live TV, Only Better. The #1 Live TV Streaming Service that lets you personalize your channel lineup and save.\nStart with the service best for you, then pick Extras in your favorite genres: Sports, Comedy, Kids, News, Movies, Lifestyle, Spanish, & more. Change your service online anytime."}]}, "developer_name": "Sling TV, LLC", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.sling.com/offer-details/disclaimers/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.sling.com/offer-details/disclaimers/terms-of-use", "publisher_name": "Sling TV, LLC", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.sling.com/", "category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED", "genres": ["MOVIE", "NEWS_AND_INFORMATION", "SPORTS"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "en_US"], "supported_input_devices": ["GEAR_VR_CONTROLLER"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "312000094276945"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 0, "nodes": []}, "baseline_offer": null, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": []}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "4417218771625802", "version": "7.3.97"}, "id": "2153329038050543", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nod